text: Moor Island, formerly Moore Island,Moor Island (Formerly Moore Island) is one of the uninhabited Arctic Archipelago islands in Kivalliq Region, Nunavut, Canada. It is one of the several islands located in Chesterfield Inlet. ==References== Category:Islands of Chesterfield Inlet Category:Uninhabited islands of Kivalliq Region Category:Islands of the Canadian Arctic Archipelago
